{"type": "article", "id": 37440, "title": "香港零售有20年来最大降幅，以及，《最终幻想》杯面来一份？ | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-02-04T02:30:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3592, "name": "The North Face"}, {"id": 20739, "name": "STUSSY"}, {"id": 37319, "name": "H&M Studio"}, {"id": 37320, "name": "日清杯面"}, {"id": 37321, "name": "香港零售业"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 1662, "name": "宫崎骏"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170204083614TpUuCJaqhGrZAmxw.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/hong-kong-2016-retail-sales-worst-decline-in-20-years/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2016 年，香港零售业达 20 年来最大降幅 </a></b>| 受赴港大陆游客及经济低迷的影响满，2016 年，全香港的零售业同比下降了  8.1%，至 4366 亿港元。根据周五发布的政府数据显示，这是继 1998 年亚洲金融危机期间香港零售业下跌 16.7% 以来，近 20 年内的最大降幅。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/fendi-approaches-millennials-with-dedicated-digital-platform-10774713/\" rel=\"nofollow\">为讨好千禧一代，Fendi 推出了全新的数字化平台</a></b> | 这个平台叫做 <font face=\"FormaText, sans-serif\">\"F is for…”，将于 2 月 6 日登陆 Fendi 的官网</font> <a href=\"http://fendi.com\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">fendi.com</a>，<font face=\"FormaText, sans-serif\">正式开始运营。</font></p><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/ralph-lauren-q3-2017-revenues-drop-12-to-1-7-billion/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Ralph Lauren 公布第三季度财报，净收入下降了 12%</b></a> | Ralph Lauren 公布 2017 财年第三季度财报，净收入下降了 12%，至 17 亿美元。该公司称，它在这一季度进行了业务调整，清理了 23% 的库存，减少了 20% 商品的库存量单位。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/lvmh-sets-up-structure-to-invest-in-emerging-luxury-brands/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LVMH 设立奢侈品牌投资基金</b></a> | 周五，奢侈品集团 LVMH 称，将设立一个奢侈品牌投资基金，专门用来投资一些小众的，有前景的生产化妆品或配件的时尚公司。这个基金的初始资本约 5000 万欧元，每笔投资的金额计划控制在 200 万至 1000 万欧元以内。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>H&amp;M 支线 H&amp;M Studio 发布 2017 春夏 lookbook。结合了传统时装剪裁但加入了如同运动服般的机能性设计，可穿性及舒适度将大大提高。与此同时，品牌还将带来全新的即看即买的体验。在 3 月 1 日巴黎时装周举办走秀之后，从 3 月 2 日起，就可以在店铺进行购买了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084005W6ug7PKpJADG4yBX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084005nNkIlQai4YrSDu83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084005H7WObqwentoE3Jpi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702040840053ANkh29uG5HqOUod.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084005wONf0ctjl8HJ3h6r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084005vXgKnkFmP1DB0VWb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084006Ube6WSJ0mCszxcRZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>街头时尚品牌<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/search?s=stussy\" rel=\"nofollow\">&nbsp;Stussy </a>发布&nbsp;2017 春季系列 Lookbook，这一次的拍摄再度找来摄影师 Tyrone Lebon 。更是特别去纽约取景来传达 Stussy New York 的生活态度和美式风格。该系列将于 2 月 10 日登陆专门店及网店。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084029aF189vRbWlyk5sCH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084029hEDR7ikOeoj9Ad3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084030E0O1qsnWAyhPM4fD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084030mGgf5QY9wzZU3BKu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084038YwkgCHN2UpoATzcP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084038tc9ETHkKwnxisYfV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084049FRTNMeGroQwsfl2i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084049Sr04iX5mbz67Uqwc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084049Da9i6StGFg4h1BEI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084100TVjrlaXFZcm5H84b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>经典游戏《最终幻想》&nbsp;30 周年庆，与日清合作推出了特别版杯面套装及巨型叉子特典。杯面套装以一套 15 个的方式限量发售，并将 1 代至 15 代大 Boss 于游戏中的样貌加入杯面包装设计上。同时，日清为了答谢支持者购买特别版杯面套装，更以《最终幻想》内的终极武器作设计灵感，打造出共 30 支长 60 厘米的叉子。这个特别版杯面套装已于<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://store.nissin.com/jp/feature/finalfantasy30th/\" rel=\"nofollow\">日清x《Final Fantasy》的专属网站</a>接受预订，定价为 5600 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084111goWp6a98lMTR2DPC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084111vOBbqVz6U1NHWYuX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666454\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084111eN84iJp37YrHMKQ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">由&nbsp;The North Face 与&nbsp;nanamica 共同打造的日本支线 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/the-north-face-purple-label-2017-spring-summer-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">The North Face Purple Label&nbsp;&nbsp;发布 2017 春夏系列</a>。该系列延续支线品牌一贯的简约风格，以深蓝、灰绿、米白等色调贯穿始终，轻量防雨外套、Smock Jacket、衬衫、T-Shirt、短裤、背包和渔夫帽等多款，营造出独有的都市机能美学。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084121G7pcePgOojJfr1xh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084130kL53sDieOmT6FqX4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084136Lj3we0CNXOHfJ5gr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084136Mrik8OvF2DGa05tf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084136AaUrCyBiu3HWPbQK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084136NHyvBsjT3Cu29aPi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017020408413651vUQ9fOluok6CgD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204084136spXFcdU2D0ZEQhiH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/the-miyazaki-art-show\" rel=\"nofollow\">旧金山的 Spoke Art Gallery 将在 2 月 4 日至 25 日间举办宫崎骏致敬画展《The Miyazaki Art Show》</a>。展览特意找来超过 50 位艺术家以吉卜力工作室的动画为创作灵感，并以雕塑、绘画、版画等不同形式制作出作品。有兴趣的话可以去看看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702040839300bNy9cxs4lkOq2uH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702040839308t5iIWc47xeYH01m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204083930jyiAXFIK3JhRH8ZL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204083931MF01aqGAb9JNkL6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204083931aQLXOljT3x1ygnGM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204083931kLsGUevBzgwWl7J9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170204083940xYho1PnDBO98XVQy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/the-north-face-purple-label-2017-spring-summer-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}